data.description: Peaceful Peoria Pool Home on Market! Premium corner lot location close to both 101 & Hwy 60, this updated ranch style home comes equipped with a rare diving pool & room for storage in the yard. Walking distance to nearby Monroe Park & both elementary & high schools. Upgrades include new kitchen (2023), floors & HVAC (2022), & bathrooms (2017). Shopping, dining, medical & extensive park system all within 5 minutes while Glendale Sports & Entertainment District to the south or Arrowhead Town Center/P83 to the north are only 10 minutes away. Come & see!
